OL,5, Parents of children with mental health 
OL,6, issues have criticised a new campaign  
OL,7, on school attendance.                  
OL,9,FThe government wants parents to send   
OL,10,Ftheir children to school if they are   
OL,11,Fworried or anxious.                    
OL,13,FKatie Berrill says her son has not     
OL,14,Fattended his secondary in Northampton  
OL,15,Ffor nearly a year due to severe OCD.   
OL,17,F"I can't begin to say how angry this   
OL,18,Fmakes me feel. It is making parents    
OL,19,Ffeel guilty. We would love our children
OL,20,Fto be able to attend school," she said.
